## 1) Foundations / Global CSS (nicht verhandelbar)

### 1.1 Text-Rendering
```css
-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
```

### 1.2 Fokus-Stile (Accessibility)
```css
*:focus-visible,
input[type="file"]:focus-visible {
  outline: 0.125rem solid #4d65ff;
  outline-offset: 0.125rem;
}
```

### 1.3 Richtext-Margin-Resets
In `.w-richtext`:
- kein Top-Margin beim ersten Element
- kein Bottom-Margin beim letzten Element

### 1.4 Container-Zentrierung (nie brechen lassen)
`.container-small`, `.container-medium`, `.container-large` bleiben zentriert:
```css
margin-right: auto !important;
margin-left: auto !important;
```

### 1.5 Text Clamp Utilities
- `.text-style-3lines` via `-webkit-line-clamp: 3`
- `.text-style-2lines` via `-webkit-line-clamp: 2`

