### 2.2 Hide-Utilities
| Klasse | Wirkung |
|---|---|
| `.hide` | `display: none !important` (immer) |
| `.hide-tablet` | ab ≤ 991px |
| `.hide-mobile-landscape` | ab ≤ 767px |
| `.hide-mobile` | ab ≤ 479px |

