## 7) Core Components

### 7.1 Navbar (Pipely-Klassen — kanonisch)

**DOM-Struktur:**
```
navbar w-nav
  main-wrapper is-nav
    padding-global is-navbar
      container-large
        navbar_content
          navbar_logo-link w-nav-brand
            navbar_logo  (SVG/img)
          nav_wrap
            nav_mobile w-nav-menu
              navbar_list
                nav_links w-nav-link        ← Haupt-Links
                nav_dropdown w-dropdown
                  nav_links is-dropdown w-dropdown-toggle
                    text-block
                    nav_link-icon w-icon-dropdown-toggle
                  nav_link-dropdown w-dropdown-list
                    nav_dropdown-wrap
                      nav_dropdown-content
                        nav_dropdown-column
                          nav_dropdown-link w-dropdown-link
          nav_buttons-wrap
            btn btn--small w-button         ← CTA (Demo/Kontakt)
          menu-button w-nav-button          ← Burger
            nav-button_line × 3
```

**Responsive-Regel:** Collapse → Burger ab "medium" Breakpoint (≤ 991px, in Webflow eingestellt).

**Typografie:**
- `navbar_logo-link` → `.standard-ui + .bold`
- `nav_links` → `.standard-ui`
- Navbar-CTA → `btn btn--small` + `.standard-ui`

### 7.2 Hero (Pipely-Klassen — kanonisch)

**DOM-Struktur:**
```
section_hero  (+ section--hero für Padding-Reset)
  img.img                          ← Hero-Hintergrundbild (eager, preload)
  padding-global padding-section-small
    container-large
      hero_content
        H1.standard-h1
        p.standard-teaser
        button-group
          btn btn--primary
          btn btn--outline
```

**Interaction:** Elemente starten mit `opacity: 0`, Einblenden via Webflow Interaction `scroll-into-view`.

**Performance:** Hero-Bild bekommt `loading="eager"` + `fetchpriority="high"` als Custom Attribute.

### 7.3 Footer (Pipely-Klassen)

**DOM-Struktur:**
```
section footer text-color-quaternary  (+ section--footer)
  padding-global padding-section-small
    container-large
      footer_top  (Grid: 3 Spalten)
        Spalte 1: Kontakt (Adresse + mailto)
        Spalte 2: Produkte (Links)
        Spalte 3: Metanavigation (Impressum/AGB/Datenschutz)
      footer_bottom
        footer_icon / icon_social-media
        p.standard-small.white-muted  ← Copyright
```

